original_client_text.markup_text:
If you have stinky armpits, you can rinse them daily with benzoyl peroxide wash or hibiclens to kill odor causing bacteria. For sweaty armpits, it is best to apply antiperspirant at night because our body temperature drops while we sleep and we sweat less as a result while we sleep.
If this doesn't help enough, you can try certian Dri and if that doesnt help, you can go to a dermatologist for a variety of excessive sweating prescription treatment options.
#dermatologist #dermtok #skintok #dermatologytips #dermatologistexplains #bodyodor #bodyodorsolution #armpitsmell #armpitsweat
@Heather Kornmehl, MD
